~ start_cow_pasture_box
Pasture Box: [[Hi|Hello|Howdy]], your animals are hungry.
Pasture Box: Would you like to feed your cows?
- Yes
	Marlow: yes, lets feed my cows
	do GameDialogueManager.action_feed_animals()
- No
	Marlow: No, not now
=> END

